    dc:creator "Wanghe, Kunyuan; Hu, Faxiang; Chen, Minhao; Luan, Xiaofeng" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Rhinogobius houheensis, a new species of freshwater goby (Teleostei: Gobiidae) from the Houhe National Nature Reserve, Hubei province, China" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397807>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397811>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397813>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397817>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397819>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397823>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397825>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397829> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397807>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Alcohol-preserved specimen of Rhinogobius houheensis sp. nov. from Hubei Province, China (holotype, BFU 190710001, male, 66.6 mm SL). (a) Lateral view, (b) dorsal view, and (c) ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4397807/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397811>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Top view of the predorsal body preserved by alcohol (paratype BFU 170723014), photographed by a stereomicroscope, from which the yellow light made the color looks a little different from the original specimen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4397811/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397813>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. The skeletal system of Rhinogobius houheensis sp. nov. Micro CT graphs of the whole body for four specimens and X-ray graph for one sample. The yellow dots, blue dots, and green dots display the location of pterygiophores and counts of the first dorsal fin, second dorsal fin, and anal fin, respectively. The red dots represent the counts of vertebrae. (a) Holotype BFU 190710001, (b) paratype BFU 190710002, (c) paratype BFU 190710003, (d) paratype BFU 190710004, and (e) paratype BFU 170723001." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4397813/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397817>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Live adults of Rhinogobius houheensis sp. nov. (a) Holotype BFU 190710001, male, and (b) paratype BFU 170723002, female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4397817/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397819>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Dorsal (a), lateral (b), and ventral (c) views of the head of Rhinogobius houheensis sp. nov. preserved by alcohol (holotype, BFU 190710001), showing cephalic sensory pores and papillae. Red circles indicate sensory canal pores; yellow dots represent sensory papillae. Abbreviations: AN, anterior nare pore; PN, posterior nare pore." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4397819/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397823>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Baixi River at Wufeng County, Hubei Province, China, the location of paratypes 170726026-170726029 of Rhinogobius houheensis sp. nov. collected." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4397823/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397825>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Sampling locality of Rhinogobius houheensis sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4397825/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397829>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Bayesian inference tree of Rhinogobius houheensis sp. nov. marked by red with its congeners based on full-length sequences of the cytochrome b gene. The values at nodes are Bayesian posterior probability values." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4397829/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

